Islamic Bank Lends Mali 11.3 Million Euros for Roads, Housing

-- B y   D i a k a r i d i a   D e m b e l e
-- 
2011-10-13T10:55:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/islamic-bank-lends-mali-11-3-million-euros-for-roads-housing.html
The  Islamic Development Bank  will
lend Mali 11.3 million euros ($15.5 million) for projects
including road drainage and improving drinking-water supplies,
the West African nation’s government said.  The loan from the  Jeddah , Saudi Arabia-based bank includes
about 8 million euros to build nearly 1,500 housing units in
Bamako, the capital, according to the administration’s
statement e-mailed yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Diakaridia Dembele in Bamako via Accra at 
 ebowers1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at   asguazzin@bloomberg.net  